Array of lead objects. Each lead must ha:
Array von Lead-Objekten. Jeder Lead muss ein "E-Mail"-Feld haben. Optionale Felder: first_name, last_name, phone_number, company_name, Website, Standort, linkedin_profile, company_url, custom_fields (object).

Beispiel:
```json
[
  {
    "email": "john@example. om",
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "company_name": "Acme Corp",
    "custom_fields": { "job_title": "CEO" }
  }
]
```
